text: I learned Ackles are generally longer/thinner birds with tails (most were purple). What about you?
An ellep is a green or yellow bug. All but one had a small head, some have wings. One had a large head with no wings. No single feature seemed to identify alone.
Sounds good. Any questions for me before we proceed?

Large blue fish (with or without whiskers) or small purple with whiskers
Lorches are green and red bugs. The green ones must have small heads to be a lorch, red ones must have big heads to be a lorch. Either can have wings or not.
Ok, thanks.
mook are yellow or orange fish WITH whiskers
This one was either too easy or misleading. Only red creatures were crulets. None were blue.
